  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK521">
<l>paṟṟaṟṟa kaṇṇum paḻaimaipā rāṭṭutal </l>
<l>cuṟṟattār kaṇṇē yuḷa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even when (a man's) property is all gone, relatives will act towards him with their accustomed (kindness).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
